<plot>By following the arguments of a heterosexual couple that don't realize that they are only Barbie dolls being manipulated by an unseen being, this four minute video explores the age old confusions of love verses lust, fate verses free will, and whether romantic relationships are as epic and dramatic as they seem, or whether they are merely venues to act out ideas acquired at childhood, and raises the question, are we ever too old to play with Barbies?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?222718</url></doc>
